{"tid":1531363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港已經唔再係法治社會","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T15:29:36.000Z","uid":166528,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1e013a5abc7d1415d448f00eec8405cffd20b032","tid":1531363,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;法治(rule of law)的內涵，不單是要求所有人民守法，更側重於法律對政府權力的控制和拘束。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;法治意味着每個人都受到法律的約束，包括立法者、行政官員和法官&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n根本政府就係帶頭破壞法治既果個，又dq又俾警隊濫權，完全凌駕於法律。但政府就成日spin去話因為市民犯法所以破壞左法治，完全係賊喊捉賊！<br />\n<br />\n宜家香港根本係一個法制(rule by law)社會。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;即法律是政府管理國家、管理社會的工具，制定法律以管束人民。把法律當做統治工具的政府會侵犯公民權利，而對應的法律應被廢除並停止執行。以法統治與保護民主自由的法治也是有區別的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n即係已經衰退到同大陸係差唔多。而衰退既源頭就係政府既腐敗！<br />\n<br />\nref: <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR22INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=373259c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BB%A5%E6%B3%95%E8%80%8C%E6%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%2580%258C%25E6%25B2%25BB&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR22INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=e9477c4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BB%A5%E6%B3%95%E8%80%8C%E6%B2%BB</a>"},{"pid":"a9c800f8d5ea614f9ff301e22e5ffe87d8eaedf0","tid":1531363,"uid":76538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">阻一阻你, 幫手入去睇下, 救下學生</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n［學校戰線］打壓學生中學名單！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1531335/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1531335/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2697f310a71d31